---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import games from '../assets/games.png';
import moviecredits from '../assets/moviecredits.png';
import scrapPlaceholder from '../assets/scrap-placeholder.png';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="VFX and Games"
  description="Dioni's work in VFX and games."
  pubDate={new Date('March 12 2026')}
  heroImage={scrapPlaceholder}
>
  <h2 class="paper">Visual Effects (VFX)</h2>

  <iframe
    class="paper"
    style="width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 16/9;"
    src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/q-ie8UhFECM"
    title="Where I Work - Framestore (Pipeline Technical Director)"
    frameborder="0"
    allowfullscreen
  ></iframe>

  <p class="paper">
    I worked in VFX industry for 12 years in London and Sydney.
    It started when I saw the early shots of Iron Man at the Lucasfilm/ILM studio
    in Singapore (I was in the Lucas game division then) and ended more than 
    a decade later when we finished Avengers: Endgame.
    I realised then that this was also the end of my game. Thank you Marvel
    for paying half of my mortgage.

    <br />Working in VFX was a blast, I loved every bit of it with all its 
    imperfections. But I knew it was time for me to do something else.
    This page is more of a record for myself and occasional friends who are interested.
    I sometimes forget which movies I've worked on, it was that many!
  </p>

  <h3 class="paper">Credits</h2>
  <ol class="paper">
    <li><a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1219342/" target="_blank">Legend of the Guardians: The Owls of Ga'Hoole</a> (2010)</li>
    <li><a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1454468/" target="_blank">Gravity</a> (2013)</li>
    <li><a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1300854/" target="_blank">Iron Man 3</a> (2013)</li>
    <li><a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2015381/" target="_blank">Guardians of the Galaxy</a> (2014)</li>
    <li><a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1109624/" target="_blank">Paddington</a> (2014)</li>
    <li><a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3659388/" target="_blank">The Martian</a> (2015)</li>
    <li><a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt4154756/" target="_blank">Avengers: Infinity War</a> (2018)</li>
    <li><a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0437086/" target="_blank">Alita: Battle Angel</a> (2019)</li>
    <li><a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt6320628/" target="_blank">Spider-Man: Far from Home</a> (2019)</li>
  </ol>

  <Image src={moviecredits} alt="Movie credits" class="paper" style="display: block; margin: 0 auto;" />
  <p class="text-center">See, I forgot to put Iron Man 3.</p>

  <h3 class="paper">Notable ones (uncredited)</h2>

