  <h3 class="paper">Featured on</h3>
  <ul class="paper">
    <li><a href="https://discovercreative.careers/students-and-parents/do-you-have-to-be-good-at-art/" target="_blank">Do you have to be good at art?</a> — Discover Creative Careers</li>
    <li><a href="https://discovercreative.careers/video-programme/screen/framestore-pipeline-technical-director/" target="_blank">Framestore Pipeline Technical Director</a> — Discover Creative Careers</li>
