  <h2 class="paper">Games</h2>

  <p class="paper">
  I worked for about 4 years in video games industry, in Melbourne and Singapore. 
  The games I worked on:
  </p>

  <ul class="paper">
    <li>Nicktoons Unite! (2005) — Nintendo GameCube and Sony PS2</li>
    <li>Nicktoons: Battle for Volcano Island (2006) — Nintendo GameCube and Sony PS2</li>
    <li>Star Wars: The Clone Wars - Jedi Alliance (2008) — Nintendo DS</li>
  </ul>

  <Image src={games} alt="Games" class="paper" style="display: block; margin: 0 auto;" />

  <p class="paper">
  Fun facts: I watched the entire three seasons of SpongeBob (plus some Danny Phantom
  and The Fairly OddParents) when I worked on the Nicktoons games.
  I also watched the entire Star Wars movies when I began working on the Clone
  Wars game (no I never watched them before that). Because research.
  </p>

</Layout>
